Global, regional, and national deaths, prevalence, disability-adjusted life 
years, and years lived with disability for chronic obstructive pulmonary disease 
and asthma, 1990-2015: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease 
Study 2015.

GBD 2015 Chronic Respiratory Disease Collaborators.

Collaborators: Soriano JB, Abajobir AA, Abate KH, Abera SF, Agrawal A, Ahmed MB, 
